Celestial Emissary (Su)		KEY:Celestial Emissary ~ Sky Dragon	SOURCEPAGE:p.98	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC: Three times per day, a great wyrm sky dragon can imbue others with the celestial aspect of the oracle spell divine vessel*, but it can only be cast on another willing creature of good alignment.
