Dogmatic Discordance (Su)	KEY:Dogmatic Discordance ~ Sovereign Dragon	SOURCEPAGE:p.100	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC: Good or evil creatures take a -2 penalty when making saving throws against a sovereign dragon's spells, spell-like abilities, breath weapon, and aura.
